schedule.text:
Desiring to improve the effectiveness of
            their co-operation in criminal matters and in the confiscation of proceeds of
            crime;

subsection.content:
the request relates to acts or omissions which
                    would not have constituted an offence under the law of the Requested Party, if
                    they had taken place within its jurisdiction;

the Requested Party has substantial grounds for
                    believing that the request has been made for the purpose of prosecuting a person
                    on account of his race, religion, nationality or political opinions;

the purpose of the request, the nature of the
                    assistance being sought and its relevance to the investigation, prosecution or
                    proceeding;

where appropriate, a description of the formalities
                    or procedures to be followed by the Requested Party in executing the request and
                    the reasons therefor;
